    {
        "content": "<p>In this case, you're using tactics to make data. The tactics are very straightforward, so it's fine here, but the idiomatic way might be:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">def</span> <span class=\"n\">square_of_comp_top_bottom'</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">A</span> <span class=\"bp\">âŸ¶</span> <span class=\"n\">B</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">g</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">B</span> <span class=\"bp\">âŸ¶</span> <span class=\"n\">X</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"n\">arrow.mk</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"bp\">â‰«</span> <span class=\"n\">g</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"bp\">âŸ¶</span> <span class=\"n\">arrow.mk</span> <span class=\"n\">g</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"n\">arrow.hom_mk</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"k\">show</span> <span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"bp\">â‰«</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">arrow.mk</span> <span class=\"n\">g</span><span class=\"o\">)</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">hom</span> <span class=\"bp\">=</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">arrow.mk</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">f</span> <span class=\"bp\">â‰«</span> <span class=\"n\">g</span><span class=\"o\">))</span><span class=\"bp\">.</span><span class=\"n\">hom</span> <span class=\"bp\">â‰«</span> <span class=\"mi\">ğŸ™</span> <span class=\"n\">X</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"kd\">by</span> <span class=\"o\">{</span> <span class=\"n\">simp</span><span class=\"o\">,</span> <span class=\"n\">obviously</span> <span class=\"o\">})</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
